#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.22"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.22:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.22:0.2"
msgid "3. Anuttariyavagga"
msgstr "3. Unsurpassable"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.22:0.3"
msgid "22. Aparihāniyasutta"
msgstr "22. Non-decline"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.22:1.1"
msgid "“Chayime, bhikkhave, aparihāniye dhamme desessāmi, taṃ suṇātha … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you these six qualities that prevent decline. …"

msgctxt "an6.22:1.2"
msgid "katame ca, bhikkhave, cha aparihāniyā dhammā?"
msgstr "And what, mendicants, are the six qualities that prevent decline?"

msgctxt "an6.22:1.3"
msgid ""
"Na kammārāmatā, na bhassārāmatā, na niddārāmatā, na saṅgaṇikārāmatā, "
"sovacassatā, kalyāṇamittatā—"
msgstr ""
"Not relishing work, talk, sleep, and company, being easy to admonish, and "
"having good friends."

msgctxt "an6.22:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cha aparihāniyā dhammā."
msgstr "These six qualities prevent decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.22:2.1"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ na parihāyiṃsu kusalehi dhammehi, "
"sabbete imeheva chahi dhammehi na parihāyiṃsu kusalehi dhammehi."
msgstr ""
"Whether in the past, future, or present, all those who have not declined in "
"skillful qualities do so because of these six qualities.”"

msgctxt "an6.22:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yepi hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ na parihāyissanti kusalehi "
"dhammehi, sabbete imeheva chahi dhammehi na parihāyissanti kusalehi dhammehi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.22:2.3"
msgid ""
"Yepi hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi na parihāyanti kusalehi dhammehi, sabbete "
"imeheva chahi dhammehi na parihāyanti kusalehi dhammehī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.22:2.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
